  "texts": [
    "In highresource settings, hospitals can leverage existing data systems and advanced imaging technologies to seamlessly incorporate AI.",
    "In low-resource settings, portable devices and cloud-based platforms offer scalable solutions.",
    "Cloudbased analysis allows clinicians in remote areas to access real-time diagnostic support, creating a network of interconnected facilities that share AI-generated insights.",
    "Publicprivate partnerships and strategic investments are critical in ensuring that these technologies are affordable and accessible to all.Despite its promise, AI faces challenges related to interpretability, bias, and privacy, which must be addressed through collaboration between technologists, clinicians, policymakers, and ethicists [51].",
